DATA REUSE NOTICE

Court rulings ingested by sententim are sourced from public-domain registries:

  · Polish court judgments (SR, SO, SA, SN) via SAOS — System Analizy
    Orzeczeń Sądowych, maintained by CeON / ICM University of Warsaw.
    Polish judicial decisions are excluded from copyright protection under
    art. 4 of the Polish Act on Copyright and Related Rights
    (ustawa o prawie autorskim i prawach pokrewnych).

  · CJEU judgments via CELLAR (Publications Office of the European Union),
    reusable under Commission Decision 2011/833/EU. NOTE: in MVP-1 the
    CJEU pipeline is gated behind the SENTENTIM_ENABLE_CJEU=1 environment
    variable and is not used by the published corpus.

Sententim does NOT redistribute the full text of judgments. The bundled DB
contains only deterministically-extracted facts (signature, court, date,
outcome class, legal basis citations) plus a sha256 of the source text and
a link back to the public source URL.
